OL,3,CMan dies after falling from Birmingham
OL,4,CChildren's Hospital
OL,6,FA man has died after falling from
OL,7,FBirmingham Children's Hospital.
OL,9,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,10,Fhospital shortly before 10am Friday
OL,11,Fmorning (July 10th).
OL,13,FBirmingham Women's and Children's NHS
OL,14,FFoundation Trust said the man was
OL,15,Fworking on construction at the
OL,16,Fhospital.
OL,18,FBSN Group Construction confirmed the
OL,19,Fincident and said their thoughts are
OL,20,Fwith the man's family and friends.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
