OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1783939847
OL,3,CMan dies after falling from Birmingham
OL,4,CChildren's Hospital
OL,6,FThey also said they are working with
OL,7,FWest Midlands Police and the Health
OL,8,Fand Safety Executive with their
OL,9,Finvestigation.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for BSN Group
OL,12,FConstruction site said: "We are
OL,13,Fsaddened to confirm that a person has
OL,14,Fdied following an incident at our
OL,15,Fconstruction site at Birmingham
OL,16,FChildren's Hospital on Friday, 10 July.
OL,18,F"Our thoughts are with their family,
OL,19,Ffriends and colleagues at this
OL,20,Fextremely difficult time.
OL,26,@zD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34503
