CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1783939847
OL,3,CMan dies after falling from Birmingham
OL,4,CChildren's Hospital
OL,6,F"We take health and safety very
OL,7,Fseriously, and we are assisting the
OL,8,Fpolice, the Health and Safety
OL,9,FExecutive and all relevant authorities
OL,10,Fwith their enquiries.
OL,12,F"As investigations are ongoing, it
OL,13,Fwould not be appropriate to comment
OL,14,Ffurther at this stage."
OL,16,FBirmingham Women's and Children's NHS
OL,17,FFoundation Trust said: "There has been
OL,18,Fan incident at a construction site at
OL,19,FBirmingham Children's Hospital.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUvD@WO]yD@XOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
