CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1783939847
OL,3,CMan dies after falling from Birmingham
OL,4,CChildren's Hospital
OL,6,F"And our sympathies are with the
OL,7,Ffamily and friends of the individual
OL,8,Finvolved. Support is being provided to
OL,9,Fthose who have been affected."
OL,11,FA spokesman for West Midlands Police
OL,12,Fsaid: "We were called to Birmingham
OL,13,FChildren's Hospital after a man is
OL,14,Funderstood to have fallen from the
OL,15,Fbuilding at just before 9.50am today
OL,16,F(10 July).
OL,18,F"The man was sadly confirmed dead a
OL,19,Fshort time later and our thoughts are
OL,20,Fwith his loved ones.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@^O]tD@GOU
